a.xlink:title: If we seriously want to cope with the fleets of our enemies, we should follow our military advisers and order the construction of the Behemoth battleship, which plans have been finished for a long time now.
The arms race can not be stopped. Our enemy already has the necessary blueprints for a new generation of battleship on hand, but so do we. We only need to order the development.

a.text: Allow to colonize a third planet

a.xlink:title: Our fleet may be growing, but we must also make sure that we advance not only quantitative but also qualitative wise. We should concentrate our resources in the research of a new battleship.

a.text: Allow to colonize a fourth planet

a.xlink:title: Once again it is time to make a step forward. Our enemies will only respect us, if we make clear to whom the ascendancy in the universe belongs. With a new class of battleships we could reinforce our intentions.
